qEn:
A client receives this element as part of the CapabilityStatement of a server:

```json
"rest": [{
  "mode": "server",
  "resource": [{
    "type": "Patient",
    "profile": "http://hl7.org/fhir/StructureDefinition/Account",
    "interaction": [
      { "code": "read" },
      { "code": "update" },
      { "code": "vread" }
    ]
  }]
}]
```

What are the supported interactions on the Patient resource?

